---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="About — Steve Kuo" description="Background, interests, and contact.">
  <section class="py-8">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-neutral-900 dark:text-neutral-100">
      About
    </h1>
  </section>

  <div class="prose dark:prose-invert">
    <p>
      I'm Steve — a software engineer interested in systems programming,
      machine learning, and quantitative finance.
    </p>

    <p>
      Most of my work sits at the intersection of these areas: building
      low-latency distributed systems, applying ML to financial data, and
      more recently, exploring agentic AI architectures.
    </p>

    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Distributed consensus and fault-tolerant systems</li>
      <li>ML for time-series and signal processing</li>
      <li>Rust, C++, and systems-level performance</li>
      <li>LLM agents and tool-use architectures</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      The best way to reach me is via email or GitHub. I'm always happy to
      chat about distributed systems, ML infrastructure, or interesting
      side projects.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
